merchant.name: WOK HEY - Funan
merchant.description:
MUST TRY: Shanghai Fried Rice, Fresh Ramen with Braised Beef and Sous Vide Egg, Fresh Udon with Seasoned Prawn, Black Pepper Fried Rice. Wok Hey serves up hearty stir-fried fares to satisfy all your cravings. The stall features a cosy seating area and ambience to make your dining experience memorable. It is located at Funan Mall (nearest train station: City Hall MRT Station). 
Source: hungrygowhere.com
